#: includes/Core/Plugin.php
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "常見問題"

#: includes/Core/Plugin.php
msgid "Does this work without Fluent Community?"
msgstr "沒有 Fluent Community 可以使用嗎？"

#: includes/Core/Plugin.php
msgid ""
"No. This plugin is specifically designed as an add-on for Fluent Community "
"and requires it to function."
msgstr ""
"不行。此外掛專為 Fluent Community 設計，需要安裝 Fluent Community 才能運作。"

#: includes/Core/Plugin.php
msgid "Can users register for events?"
msgstr "使用者可以報名活動嗎？"

#: includes/Core/Plugin.php
msgid ""
"Not in this basic version. FCA Events Basic is for displaying events only. "
"For registration and ticketing, check out our premium version."
msgstr ""
"基本版不支援。FCA Events Basic 僅供顯示活動使用。如需報名和票務功能，請參考我"
"們的進階版本。"

#: includes/Core/Plugin.php
msgid "How do drafts work?"
msgstr "草稿如何運作？"

#: includes/Core/Plugin.php
msgid ""
"When editing a published event, you can click \"Save as Draft\" to create a "
"child draft. The original event stays live while you work on changes. When "
"ready, publish the draft to merge changes back into the original event."
msgstr ""
"編輯已發布的活動時，可點擊「儲存為草稿」建立子草稿。原始活動保持上線，您可在"
"草稿中進行修改。準備好後，發布草稿即可將變更合併回原始活動。"

#: includes/Core/Plugin.php
msgid "Is it multisite compatible?"
msgstr "支援多站台嗎？"

#: includes/Core/Plugin.php
msgid "Yes, you can activate it on individual sites in a multisite network."
msgstr "可以，您可以在多站台網路的個別站台上啟用。"

